[[Afaylu:Berber_flag.svg|thumb|350px|Acnyal amaziɣ]] '''Acnyal amaziɣ''' iga yan ucnyal isffuɣ-t-id [[Agraw imaziɣen|ugraw n imaziɣn]] ( ma mu tinin s tfransist : l'Académie berbère ) ɣ isggʷasn n 70's ɣ ammas n tmazirt n [[Fransa]]. Mac ɣ usggʷas n [[1998]], rat issrṣu [[Agraw amaḍlan amaziɣ|Ugraw Amaḍlan Amaziɣ]] (GMM) lli igan agraw nnsn amnzu ɣ [[Tigzirin tiknariyin|Tigzirin Tiknariyin]] ɣ tmazirt n [[Sblyun]]<ref>(ar) Asit n Hespress, Amgrad yuratt ufaylasuf Ahmad Asid :https://web.archive.org/web/20170922093131/http://www.hespress.com/writers/55571.html</ref>. Acnyal amaziɣ iga-d ɣila yan ucnyal ilan atig imqqurn dar imaziɣn n tafriqt n ugafa ula ɣ imaziɣn n umaḍal.<ref>(fr) Asit n Amazighworld :http://www.amazighworld.org/news/index_show.php?id=690</ref>

Iga 30 ɣuct n ku usggʷas ass amaḍlan n ucnyal amaziɣ.

== Aglam ==
Gis krad ikʷlan: Aẓerwal, azegzaw d awraɣ. Ɣ tuẓẓumt nns ittwars usekkil n aza neɣ yaz « ⵣ » s aklu azggʷaɣ s tirra n [[Tifinaɣ]]<ref>(en) Asit n Crwflags : https://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/xb.html</ref>.

* Aẓrwal anamk nns igat yill agrakal d yill aṭlasi;
* Azgzaw anamk nns igat idrarn d izaɣaren izgzawn n Tafriqt n ugafa ;
* Awraɣ anamk nns igat tiniri nɣ tanzruft imqqurn n Tafriqt Ugafa .
